{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC16_RAN_080.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x17,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "*sigh* I never noticed it this whole time...but it seems like I'm not very lucky."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What's wrong?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Don't worry, It's fine. That doesn't really mean anything..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "(I-I wonder why he's pouting...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Did Ernie force you to work against your will again?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Nope. I wouldn't get this depressed from that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Then, did you drop your wallet somewhere...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Do I seem that childish to you...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe6,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "In the end, I wasn't able to see that legendary flower with my own eyes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Oh, but thanks to you, I was able to see it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "It was really pretty...but, don't get so depressed."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure there'll be a next time.<CR>And when it comes, you'll definitely<CR>see it...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I wonder... For another solar eclipse to happen like that, by my calculations..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x188,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "It'll be in the spring, 52 years from now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "That long...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Yes. I'll be an 80 year old grandpa!<CR>At that age, the real mystery will<CR>be how I'm still alive..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Th-That's not true. I'm sure if you work hard for it, you'll be fine...I think!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Even if I do live till then, I wonder if I'll still have the desire to sing about that flower..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe8,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "O, the world has been engulfed in darkness. It's like the poet inside me has already died!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "The gods are so unfair... Ayesha, can you at least describe the flower to me in detail?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Of course. Umm, let's see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "(Hmm, I was able to see the flower thanks to Ranun, so this is the least I can do.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "(But this might take a while...)"
        }
    ]
}